sentences: Polani (Hebrew: נעמי פולני; born August 4, 1927) is an Israeli musical director, theater director, singer, producer, actress, and dancer.
She is the Israel Prize laureate for Theater and Dance in 2019.
Polani founded the singing group "HaTarnegolim" ("The Roosters") in 1960, and was in charge of musical and acting direction, and choreography.
Over 30 years later, Polani worked with a new group to create a comeback of the group.
